{"tid":2036380,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"海關拘捕健身中心人員　涉以威嚇手法迫消費者購買服務","createTime":"2020-05-26T12:10:10.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-30T10:29:07.000Z","uid":240250,"like":10,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"47474680ffbf328be3e16594994c157dfc16c476","tid":2036380,"uid":240250,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:10:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528390-20200526.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528390-20200526.htm&d=SVgHbq7l0Cva0E6q1evMA4TtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=c4aedcf5\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1528390-20200526.htm&h=3037057f\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1528390-20200526.htm</a><br />\n<br />\n海關拘捕一名旺角健身中心的董事及兩名銷售人員，指他們涉嫌以具威嚇性的銷售手法，迫使消費者購買健身服務合約。涉案合約總值超過90萬元，是《商品說明條例》自2013年修訂以來，海關偵破有關健身中心不良營商手法的案件中，損失金額最大的單一事主。<br />\n<br />\n海關本月中展開代號「破風」行動，打擊健身中心不良營商手法。過去數日，在旺角一間健身中心採取行動。<br />\n<br />\n海關稍後會召開記者會，交代行動詳情。"},{"pid":"c5fb129a7287d7f37cf3345d44d3258b81cd6f89","tid":2036380,"uid":177213,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:11:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5dToLrz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5dToLrz.png&h=520ea47f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/n84bUjV.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fn84bUjV.png&h=28b1c6d8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/z4ZrJdf.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fz4ZrJdf.png&h=392ae503&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"fcbe23d88ca05f193f017bd57ee8a2b2897c0828","tid":2036380,"uid":240250,"like":5,"dislike":3,"score":2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-05-26T12:16:48.000Z","msg":"香港既健身風氣真係比班敗類搞衰哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dea